Welcome to Cadencia Cycling Club (CCC). CCC is a site for cyclists world wide to connect and share their ride data. Upon creating an account, cyclists can upload their ride data (distance traveled in kilometers, minutes ridden, and date of ride). CCC will then take that information, calculate the speed of your ride in kilometers per hour, and then posted it to the rides board. Cyclists can get in conact with each other by email. The email addresses of each cyclist are listed in their user profile.


